Package: pava
Type: Package
Title: PAVA for general convex functions
Version: 0.0-7
Date: 2008-05-09
Author: Kurt Hornik, Jan de Leeuw, Patrick Mair
Maintainer: Kurt Hornik <kurt.hornik@wu-wien.ac.at>
Description: This package extends the classical pool-adjacent-violators algorithm (PAVA) for monotonic regression in terms of specifications of general convex functions, repeated measurements, observation weights, and various algorithms for handling ties. 
License: GPL
